While it mentions how many Groups and Application it is in, it does not list out the details of it. In addition, while we could see Project Roles from the UI, it is not possible yet to get such information using REST API as well.

h3. Suggested Solution:
Including those information about Groups and Application Roles will be great just like how we looking it on the UI side. If possible, including the roles as well on the list or creating another REST API for it.

